 messages - happy labor day email banner with a flag, grill, and lawn chair\" width=\"600\" height=\"200\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-63628\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/labor-day-messages-email-headers-5.png 600w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/labor-day-messages-email-headers-5-480x160.png 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 600px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p><a id=\"closed\"><\/a><\/p>\n<h2>Closed for Labor Day email templates<\/h2>\n<p>Closing for the holiday? Use these <a href=\"https:\/\/localiq.com\/blog\/small-business-email-examples-and-templates\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">email templates<\/a> to let your customers know.<\/p>\n<h3>Basic template<\/h3>\n<p>Hi all!<\/p>\n<p>Just a heads up that we\u2019ll be closed from ____ to ____ for Labor Day weekend. We hope you\u2019re taking the day off too. You deserve it! Thanks for keeping our business and the world turning!<\/p>\n<p>***<\/p>\n<h3>Fun template<\/h3>\n<p>Hi everyone,<\/p>\n<p>We wanted to let you know that we\u2019ll be closed from ____ to ____. We\u2019ll be relaxin\u2019 n\u2019 rechargin\u2019 for Labor Day weekend. But don\u2019t worry, we\u2019ll be rearin\u2019 to go on Tuesday\u2014we can only go so long without seeing your smiling faces.<\/p>\n<p>See you then!<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/labor-day-messages-email-headers-2.png\" alt=\"labor day messages - happy labor day email banner with red white and blue bunting\" width=\"600\" height=\"200\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-63631\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/labor-day-messages-email-headers-2.png 600w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/labor-day-messages-email-headers-2-480x160.png 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 6